<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>INSOMNIA — 3:00 AM</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #050508;
    --red: #c0392b;
    --red-glow: #ff2a1a;
    --dim-red: #7a1a1a;
    --cream: #e8ddd0;
    --muted: #5a4a4a;
    --white: #f0e8e8;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  /* ── CURSOR ── */
  #cursor {
    position: fixed;
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    background: var(--red-glow);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 0 18px var(--red-glow), 0 0 40px rgba(255,42,26,0.4);
  }
  #cursor-ring {
    position: fixed;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.5);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transition: left 0.12s ease, top 0.12s ease;
  }

  /* ── GRAIN ── */
  .grain {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 1000; pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.08;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 512 512' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.75' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    background-size: 200px 200px;
    animation: grain-shift 0.3s steps(2) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes grain-shift {
    0% { transform: translate(0,0); }
    25% { transform: translate(-3px,2px); }
    50% { transform: translate(2px,-3px); }
    75% { transform: translate(-2px,-2px); }
    100% { transform: translate(3px,2px); }
  }

  /* ── SCANLINES ── */
  .scanlines {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 999; pointer-events: none;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      transparent 0px, transparent 3px,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.08) 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) 4px
    );
  }

  /* ── VIGNETTE ── */
  .vignette {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 998; pointer-events: none;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, transparent 35%, rgba(0,0,0,0.85) 100%);
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  #hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center; align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .clock-strip {
    position: absolute; top: 2rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.35em; color: var(--dim-red);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    animation: flicker 5s infinite;
  }

  #live-clock {
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--red-glow);
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,42,26,0.6), 0 0 80px rgba(255,42,26,0.2);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
    animation: pulse-clock 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-clock {
    0%, 100% { text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,42,26,0.6), 0 0 80px rgba(255,42,26,0.2); }
    50% { text-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255,42,26,0.9), 0 0 120px rgba(255,42,26,0.4); }
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 8rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 0.9;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: rise 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: rise 1s ease 0.8s forwards;
  }

  @keyframes rise {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* Floating thought bubbles in hero */
  .thought-bubble {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--dim-red);
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    font-style: italic;
    animation: bubble-float linear forwards;
  }
  @keyframes bubble-float {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(0) scale(0.9); }
    15% { opacity: 0.7; }
    85% { opacity: 0.4; }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-80px) scale(1.05); }
  }

  /* Scroll indicator */
  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute; bottom: 2.5rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    animation: blink 3s infinite;
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px; height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--dim-red), transparent);
    animation: grow-line 3s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes grow-line {
    0%, 100% { height: 20px; opacity: 0.3; }
    50% { height: 40px; opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* ── SECTIONS SHARED ── */
  section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 7rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    color: var(--dim-red);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
  }
  .section-label::before {
    content: '';
    display: block; width: 40px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--dim-red);
  }

  /* ── SYMPTOMS ── */
  #symptoms { padding-top: 4rem; }

  .symptoms-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .symptom-card {
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.1);
    background: rgba(5,5,8,0.8);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background 0.4s;
  }
  .symptom-card:hover { background: rgba(122,26,26,0.12); }
  .symptom-card:hover .symptom-num { color: var(--red-glow); }

  .symptom-num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(192,57,43,0.2);
    line-height: 1;
    transition: color 0.4s;
  }
  .symptom-title {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  .symptom-desc {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ── TIMELINE ── */
  #timeline { border-top: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15); }

  .big-heading {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .big-heading span { color: var(--red-glow); }

  .timeline-track {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.2);
  }

  .tl-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-20px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .tl-item.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }

  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2.35rem;
    top: 0.35rem;
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    background: var(--dim-red);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--red-glow);
  }
  .tl-time {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--dim-red);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .tl-event {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .tl-detail {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── MIND STATIC ── */
  #mind-static {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .static-thoughts {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .static-word {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(192,57,43,0.08);
    white-space: nowrap;
    animation: drift linear infinite;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  @keyframes drift {
    from { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    to { transform: translateX(100vw); }
  }

  .static-center {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .static-center h2 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .static-center p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 2;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* ── EYE SECTION ── */
  #eye-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.1);
  }

  .eye-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 60px;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .big-eye {
    width: 160px; height: 75px;
    background: #000;
    border: 2px solid var(--red-glow);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 40px #330000,
                0 0 20px rgba(255,42,26,0.3),
                0 0 60px rgba(255,42,26,0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: eye-twitch 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes eye-twitch {
    0%, 95%, 100% { transform: scaleY(1); }
    96% { transform: scaleY(0.05); }
    97% { transform: scaleY(1); }
  }

  .big-pupil {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 30px; height: 30px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #ff1a00 0%, #800000 60%, #000 100%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 25px var(--red-glow);
    animation: pupil-drift 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pupil-drift {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
    25% { transform: translate(-35%, -55%); }
    50% { transform: translate(-60%, -45%); }
    75% { transform: translate(-45%, -60%); }
  }

  .eye-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--dim-red);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ── STATS BAR ── */
  #stats {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15);
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .stats-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .stat-item { text-align: center; }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--red-glow);
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,42,26,0.4);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .footer-text {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--dim-red);
  }
  .footer-sub {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* ── UTILS ── */
  @keyframes flicker {
    0%, 95%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    96% { opacity: 0.2; }
    97% { opacity: 0.9; }
    98% { opacity: 0.1; }
    99% { opacity: 0.8; }
  }
  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.3; }
  }

  /* ── MORNING MODE ── */
  body.morning {
    --black: #fdf6ee;
    --red: #c8855a;
    --red-glow: #e8924a;
    --dim-red: #c8855a;
    --cream: #3a2a1a;
    --muted: #8a7060;
    --white: #fff8f0;
    background: #fdf6ee;
    color: #3a2a1a;
  }
  body.morning .grain { opacity: 0.03; filter: sepia(1); }
  body.morning .vignette { background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, transparent 40%, rgba(255,220,170,0.4) 100%); }
  body.morning .scanlines { opacity: 0.3; }
  body.morning #live-clock {
    color: #e8924a;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(232,146,74,0.4), 0 0 60px rgba(232,146,74,0.1);
    animation: none;
  }
  body.morning .big-eye {
    border-color: #e8924a;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 40px #f5d5a0, 0 0 20px rgba(232,146,74,0.2);
  }
  body.morning .big-pupil {
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #e8924a 0%, #c8855a 60%, #8a5530 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(232,146,74,0.5);
  }
  body.morning #cursor { background: #e8924a; box-shadow: 0 0 18px #e8924a; }
  body.morning #cursor-ring { border-color: rgba(232,146,74,0.5); }
  body.morning .symptom-card { background: rgba(255,248,240,0.8); }
  body.morning .symptom-card:hover { background: rgba(232,146,74,0.08); }
  body.morning .marquee-item { color: #c8855a; }

  /* morning sunrise overlay */
  #morning-overlay {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 990; pointer-events: none;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 110%, rgba(255,180,80,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 3s ease;
  }
  body.morning #morning-overlay { opacity: 1; }

  /* morning text swap */
  .night-text { display: block; }
  .morning-text { display: none; }
  body.morning .night-text { display: none; }
  body.morning .morning-text { display: block; }

  /* ── CONTROL BUTTONS ── */
  #controls {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 2rem; right: 2rem;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;
    z-index: 5000;
  }

  .ctrl-btn {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(5,5,8,0.85);
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.3);
    color: var(--dim-red);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .ctrl-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(122,26,26,0.3);
    border-color: var(--red-glow);
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .ctrl-btn.active {
    background: rgba(122,26,26,0.4);
    border-color: var(--red-glow);
    color: var(--red-glow);
  }
  body.morning .ctrl-btn {
    background: rgba(253,246,238,0.9);
    border-color: rgba(200,133,90,0.4);
    color: #c8855a;
  }
  body.morning .ctrl-btn:hover, body.morning .ctrl-btn.active {
    background: rgba(232,146,74,0.15);
    border-color: #e8924a;
    color: #3a2a1a;
  }

  .ctrl-icon { font-size: 0.85rem; }

  /* morning mode transition on all colors */
  body, .symptom-card, #live-clock, .big-eye, .big-pupil,
  .section-label, .tl-dot, .stat-num, .footer-text,
  .grain, .vignette, #cursor, #cursor-ring {
    transition: background 2.5s ease, color 2.5s ease,
                border-color 2.5s ease, box-shadow 2.5s ease,
                text-shadow 2.5s ease, opacity 2.5s ease;
  }

  /* ── HORIZONTAL MARQUEE ── */
  .marquee-wrap {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15);
    padding: 1rem 0;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  .marquee-track {
    display: flex; gap: 3rem;
    animation: marquee 20s linear infinite;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .marquee-item {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--dim-red);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .marquee-dot { color: var(--red-glow); margin: 0 0.5rem; }
  @keyframes marquee {
    from { transform: translateX(0); }
    to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="grain"></div>
<div class="scanlines"></div>
<div class="vignette"></div>
<div id="morning-overlay"></div>
<div id="cursor"></div>
<div id="cursor-ring"></div>

<!-- CONTROLS -->
<div id="controls">
  <button class="ctrl-btn" id="sound-btn" onclick="toggleSound()">
    <span class="ctrl-icon" id="sound-icon">🔇</span>
    <span id="sound-label">Ambient Sound</span>
  </button>
  <button class="ctrl-btn" id="morning-btn" onclick="toggleMorning()">
    <span class="ctrl-icon" id="morning-icon">🌙</span>
    <span id="morning-label">Night Mode</span>
  </button>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<div id="hero">
  <div class="clock-strip">Current time —</div>
  <div id="live-clock">3:47 AM</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span class="night-text">Insomnia</span>
    <span class="morning-text">Morning</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    <span class="night-text">When the night refuses to end</span>
    <span class="morning-text">You made it through the dark</span>
  </p>

  <div class="scroll-hint">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    scroll
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MARQUEE -->
<div class="marquee-wrap">
  <div class="marquee-track" id="marquee">
    <span class="marquee-item">can't sleep <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">thoughts racing <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">3:00 AM again <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">eyes wide open <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">just five more minutes <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">ceiling staring back <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">body tired, mind awake <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">why am I awake <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <!-- duplicate for seamless -->
    <span class="marquee-item">can't sleep <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">thoughts racing <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">3:00 AM again <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">eyes wide open <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">just five more minutes <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">ceiling staring back <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">body tired, mind awake <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">why am I awake <span class="marquee-dot">·</span></span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SYMPTOMS -->
<section id="symptoms">
  <div class="section-label">What it feels like</div>
  <div class="symptoms-grid">
    <div class="symptom-card">
      <div class="symptom-num">01</div>
      <div class="symptom-title">Hypervigilance</div>
      <div class="symptom-desc">Every sound becomes enormous. The hum of the fridge. A car outside. Your own heartbeat.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="symptom-card">
      <div class="symptom-num">02</div>
      <div class="symptom-title">Racing Thoughts</div>
      <div class="symptom-desc">Your mind rehearses old conversations, solves tomorrow's problems, replays every mistake.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="symptom-card">
      <div class="symptom-num">03</div>
      <div class="symptom-title">Time Distortion</div>
      <div class="symptom-desc">An hour feels like five minutes. Five minutes feel like an eternity. The clock lies.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="symptom-card">
      <div class="symptom-num">04</div>
      <div class="symptom-title">The Almost</div>
      <div class="symptom-desc">That moment of falling — then a jolt. Back awake. Start again. The hypnic jerk betrayal.</div>
