<!-- MIND STATIC -->
<div id="mind-static">
  <div class="static-thoughts" id="static-thoughts"></div>
  <div class="static-center">
    <h2>The mind doesn't have an off switch.</h2>
    <p>
      Insomnia is not just the absence of sleep.<br/>
      It is presence — full, excruciating presence —<br/>
